   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Lucius Valerius Valerianus, phylarch of the present 1st year, from Aurelii Paas son of Moros, his mother Athenarous, from the city of Oxyrhynchos and his wife Athenarous daughter of Pekysis, from the same city.  We wish to have registered for the first time from now on in the house which belongs to us in the amphodon of Hippeon [Parembole] . . .</ab>
         </div>
